My Meme

It is about naruto crying about his friend sasuke, its from the Naruto Manga by Masashi Kishimoto. The joke is about how in the second part of the story, his main goal is to find sasuke, becoming most of his issues, basically ignoring his other friends.

zenmeme

library(magick)

#Image sourced from internet
crying <- image_read(path = '~/Documents/Naruto.jpg')


fortext <- image_blank(width = 500, height = 500, color = "#FAFAFA") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "I have 99 problems, Sasuke is all of them")

zenmeme <- c(crying,fortext)

image_append(zenmeme) 

image_write(zenmeme, "zenmeme.png")

My Animated GIF

The naruto manga is quite long, so you end up seeing naruto age as the story progresses, which is what the GIF shows.

naruto

library(magick)
#pictures of naruto
baby <- image_read(path = '~/Documents/babynaruto.jpeg') 
kid <- image_read(path = '~/Documents/kidnaruto.jpg')

teen <- image_read(path = '~/Documents/teennaruto.jpg')

adult <- image_read(path = '~/Documents/adultnaruto.jpg')


frame1 <- baby 
frame2 <- kid 
frame3 <- teen 
frame4 <- adult 

frame1
frame2
frame3
frame4

frames <- c(frame1, frame2, frame3, frame4)

narutoanimation <-image_animate(image_scale(frames, "200x200"), fps = 1)

image_write(narutoanimation, "naruto.gif")
